title: AmdaPark

creator: SMP Mobitech Pvt Ltd
descriptionHtml:
AmdaPark is India's Award Winning First Smart Parking Application.

AmdaPark is being used at 25+ parking locations across Ahmedabad City, and it will be used in 125+ Ahmedabad Municipal Corporation owned parking locations across Ahmedabad in a phase wise manner.

The AmdaPark app is there to address the problem of parking, in turn reducing environmental concerns and congestion provided by ShowMyParking. Since we are an IoT-based one-of-a-kind platform, parking operations have become hassle-free for the commuters.

AmdaPark is a mobile application where user can search, book and park for the available parking slots in order to park their vehicle. Basically, there will be two types of users, End User and Merchant. End user will be able to Search, Book and Park for the parking space. Merchant will be able to host their free/paid parking space in order to earn through mobile application.

AmdaPark application helps to solve the parking problems for the citizen or the End users in the smart city through digitisation based on AI and IoT technology.

creator: SMP Mobitech Pvt Ltd
descriptionHtml:
AmdaPark is India's Award Winning First Smart Parking Application.

AmdaPark is being used at 25+ parking locations across Ahmedabad City, and it will be used in 125+ Ahmedabad Municipal Corporation owned parking locations across Ahmedabad in a phase wise manner.

The AmdaPark app is there to address the problem of parking, in turn reducing environmental concerns and congestion provided by ShowMyParking. Since we are an IoT-based one-of-a-kind platform, parking operations have become hassle-free for the commuters.

AmdaPark is a mobile application where user can search, book and park for the available parking slots in order to park their vehicle. Basically, there will be two types of users, End User and Merchant. End user will be able to Search, Book and Park for the parking space. Merchant will be able to host their free/paid parking space in order to earn through mobile application.

AmdaPark application helps to solve the parking problems for the citizen or the End users in the smart city through digitisation based on AI and IoT technology.

Powered By
Show My Parking
